      "message": "\u003e Should this stay in Chromium?\n\nWell, you did bring over the BUILD and mini_chromium change to fake-make this work? It’s fine in that case.\n\nIf you wanted to, you could put in util/BUILD.gn:\n\n  configs \u003d [ \"../build:crashpad_is_in_chromium\" ]\n  \nwhich would give you the ability to do\n\n  #if defined(OS_LINUX) || (CRASHPAD_IS_IN_CHROMIUM \u0026\u0026 BUILDFLAGS(IS_CHROMEOS_LACROS))\n  \nif needed. I don’t know if it’s so important, though. I like to minimize the use of CRASHPAD_IS_IN_CHROMIUM.",
